{{Quote|Well... I hope you can do something!! Ha ha ha! All of this laughing is beginning to hurt! Ha ha ha! Owww!!|[[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]] to [[Wicket Wystri Warrick/Legends|Wicket]]|<ref name="Ewoks 7">[[Ewoks (1985) 7|''Ewoks'' (1985) 7]]</ref>}}
The '''perilous laughing spell''' was a [[Magic/Legends|magic]] spell contracted by touching a [[loonee bird]]. It caused the unfortunate victim to laugh uncontrollably, a spell that could plague its victim forever and would temporarily affect any who went near them. Only the tears from [[Mount Sorrow]] could cure the spell. The [[Ewok/Legends|Ewok]] poet, [[Teebo/Legends|Teebo]], was once affected by the spell, but was eventually cured by Mount Sorrow's tears.

